text: I received a very weird invite to "The last 2014 Intel® RealSense™ (free) Hacker Lab in the US" which takes place on Thu 12/18 at Urban Studio (NW 9th and Davis). It's a morning/lunch event, so I'm not planning to go, but happy to forward the invite if anyone is interested. I understand there are giveaways of the realsense camera dev edition as part of the event. (But they want RSVPs from people with certain types of coding experience.)
A bit late - but you can still get on the waitlist for creative mornings <http://creativemornings.com/talks/jen-delos-reyes>
